ActRoyal Canadian Mounted Police Act
SubjectMunicipal Police Services Agreements with Blackfalds, Alberta and Redcliff, Alberta
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness, on behalf of the Government of Canada, enter into arrangements with the towns of BLACKFALDS, ALBERTA and REDCLIFF, ALBERTA, for the use or employment of the ROYAL CANADIAN MOUNTED POLICE in aiding the administration of justice in those municipalities and in carrying into effect the laws in force there.
